	<li><a href="http://h10025.www1.hp.com/ewfrf/wc/softwareDownloadIndex?cc=us&lc=en&dlc=en&softwareitem=ob-105185-1">Wireless - LAN</a> - Atheros AR9485 802.11b/g/n Wireless LAN Driver Lite care of HP.com
